s no turns-* outputs and no actual benchmark results.**\n\nWhat the files actually show:\n\n- `watchdog.log` (line 1): Started watching `D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\mbti\\agent\\benchmark_runs\\full-20260510` (not `multi-turn-20260511`).\n- `watchdog.log` (line 2): \"watched 80-turn run completed; no fallback needed\" — the watchdog detected that the prior `full-20260510` 80-turn run finished successfully.\n- `watchdog-status.json`: Status `completed_existing`, referencing the same `full-20260510` watch directory, updated at `2026-05-11T01:26:04`.\n\n**No new 80-turn test was started in `multi-turn-20260511`.** The directory was created by the watchdog process, but it monitored the already-completed `full-20260510` run and found it done — so no fallback runs (20/40/60/80) were triggered.\n\nThe actual completed 80-turn run lives in `D:\\agent_workspace\\projects\\mbti\\agent\\benchmark_runs\\full-20260510/`, with all 4 MBTI personas (`enfp_spark`, `estp_operator`, `intj_architect`, `isfj_keeper`) producing `conversation_result.json` and `questionnaire_result.json`.\n</answer>\n\n<next_steps>\n- If you intended to start a fresh `multi-turn-20260511` run, the watchdog was pointed at the wrong directory. Verify the watchdog configuration for the intended run path.\n- If you want to inspect the completed `full-20260510` results, they are in `agent/benchmark_runs/full-20260510/`.\n</next_steps>","metadata":{"truncated":false,"task_id":"bg_a876a9c8","agent":"explore","category":"","description":"Inspect benchmark outputs","sessionId":"ses_1eca50501ffe10qYY7FRjx2K4s"},"title":"explore - Inspect benchmark outputs","time":{"start":1778441256144,"end":1778441256157}},"id":"prt_e135bfa950010anHrtlpcJgN5O","sessionID":"ses_1eca52b09ffeuVhAIMzMl44cQF","messageID":"msg_e135beeab001a1cRT7Av13Y30w"}}
